		<item>
		<title>SAFETY ALERT: Refurbished H20 found in Nigeria</title>
		<link>https://www.cmhammar.com/safety-alert-refurbished-h20-found-in-nigeria/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Mikael Lundholm]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 13:13:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Bulletin]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.cmhammar.com/?p=10389</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>Dear Valued Customer, We have recently become aware that refurbished versions of our H20 Hydrostatic Release Unit for Rafts are being circulated on the Nigerian market. A refurbished unit is a product that originates from Hammar but has been polished, modified and sold as a new. As your safety is our top priority, we urge...</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com/safety-alert-refurbished-h20-found-in-nigeria/">SAFETY ALERT: Refurbished H20 found in Nigeria</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com">Hammar</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Dear Valued Customer,<br />
We have recently become aware that refurbished versions of our H20 Hydrostatic Release Unit for Rafts are being circulated on the Nigerian market. A refurbished unit is a product that originates from Hammar but has been polished, modified and sold as a new. As your safety is our top priority, we urge you to take the following precautions:</p>
<ol>
<li>Verify Product Authenticity: Ensure that the safety equipment you purchase is from an authorized dealer. Check for our official branding, serial numbers and check validity using the MarCode App. More information <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com/h20-release-units/#marcode">https://www.cmhammar.com/h20-release-units/#marcode</a>.</li>
<li>Inspect Equipment: Before use, inspect the equipment for any signs of wear, damage, or tampering.</li>
<li>Report Suspicious Products: If you suspect that you have purchased a refurbished product, please contact Hammar immediately for verification and further instructions.</li>
</ol>
<p>Using non-authentic or refurbished safety equipment can pose serious risks. For your safety and peace of mind, always choose genuine products from authorized sources.</p>
<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our Technical Sales.</p>
<p>Thank you for your attention to this important matter.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.cmhammar.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/250228-Safety-Alert-Refurbished-H20-found-in-Nigeria-1.pdf">250228 Safety Alert, Refurbished H20 found in Nigeria</a></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com/safety-alert-refurbished-h20-found-in-nigeria/">SAFETY ALERT: Refurbished H20 found in Nigeria</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com">Hammar</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
